both front and rear. the handset packs an 8 mp resolution (f/2.2 aperture) rear camera with led flash. coolpad mega 2.5d also sports an 8 mp resolution selfie snapper with f/2.2 aperture and 83-degree wide-angle lens. both the cameras are tailored to shoot videos with 700p resolution at 30 fps. the camera ui features â€˜smart beautificationâ€™ mode that offers more than a handful of customization options while snapping selfies. coolpad mega 2.5d includes a 5.5-inch hd (1280x720 p) resolution ips lcd display with a pixel density of 267 ppi. the handset looks quite attractive with a scratch resistant, 2.5d curved glass layered on top of the display panel, a metal side frame, and an eye-catching plastic back panel offers a premium sense, lookswise. coolpad mega 2.5d is powered by a 1ghz quad-core mediatek mt6735p processor teamed with 3gb ram, mali t720 gpu and 16gb of onboard multimedia storage (expandable up to 32gb via microsd card). the handset runs coolpadâ€™s custom cool ui 8.0 on top of android v6.0 (marshmallow) . the device encapsulates a 2,500 mah battery to fuel its chipset. it also supports dual sim cards (nano + nano). other basic features and connectivity options include 4g-lte, wi-fi (both direct and hotspot), bluetooth 4.0, a-gps, microusb otg and fm radio.',2,0,'amazone'),(4,'positive','ðÿ‘‰design and build the mega 2.5d is certainly an attractive looking phone in its gold avatar and we can see coolpad has paid close attention to the build as well as fit and finish of the chassis. ðÿ‘‰specifications and software - under the hood, we have a mediatek mt6735p quad-core soc, which honestly, isnt the best choice in this day and age. any other budget chipset from qualcomm would be better. it comes with 3 gb of ram which no other brand will give at this price . it comes with the latest android marshmallow which is good to see. ðÿ‘‰performance - display performance is quite good in terms of colour reproduction and sunlight legibility although the ambient light sensor is a bit slow to react at times.call quality is good but the volume level of the speaker is too weak for a telephone call. ðÿ‘‰ camera - the phone has 8-megapixel cameras for the front and rear, both of which do an average job at best. ðÿ‘‰ battery - the battery is just okay. as it doesnt last for a full day. overall just a decent phone. better options available.',4,0,'amazone'),(4,'negative','ye set hai achaa per iski pareshnai hai hai ki isme 2 sim sath nahi lag sakti agar 2 sim lagao toh card nahi laga sakte agar 1 sim lagao toh card laga sakte magar ek baar me 3 no cheeze nahilaga sakte hai islyy i m not satisfied thiss coolpad megaa 2.5d',0,2,'amazone'),(4,'negative','i purchased this from amazon and its working fine till today almost 3 months gone from today, yesterday i dont know suddenly there touch is not working i tried lot from my side but couldnt do any thing and finally today i visited there service centre and they said we have to send this out of station and it will come after 20 days and its minimum time and it can delay also. my point is how can i leave with phone of 20 days i dont have any alternative so this is very bad service quality by the service centre. hope for well that it.',0,4,'amazone'),(5,'positive','i am using this mobile. i was using earlier sony xperia m5 (rs 25000/-). this m.obile is even better than sony xperia m5 surprisingly. no battery heating no hanging better audio and speaker performance than sony xperia. loved it and cost ios only rs 3499',4,0,'amazone'),(5,'positive','im writing this review after using it since last 1 month 1) built quality design is from front is not so much impressive. ring at back gives it unique leave. sandstone finishing gives it comfortable grip. bezel at front bottom shines. overall built quality and design is descent. 2) display display is ips lcd hd. it is very bright. too much saturated. it results in production dull colours. display is reflective but higher brightness level allows you to read display comfortably even in direct sunlight. texts appear on screen are very crisp and clear. user definitely gets delighted while browsing and reading on scree. touch is okay. it struggles while detecting minor touches. viewing angles are also good. asahi dragaontrail glass gives display solidness and resists minor scratches and no need to put any extra screen guard. 3) call quality it supports only 3g and not 4g. it has two separate sim slots with separate memory slot. 1st sim slot supports nano sim while 2nd one supports micro sim. network reception is good. call quality is also nice and and front speaker is also loud so you can clearly listen voice even in traffic noise. 4) camera keep your camera quality expectations while considering price tag. both the cameras are of 5mp. rear camera supports hdr, face beauty mode and gesture detection feature. rear camera quality is very average. again colour production is dull and camptures lot of noise. pictures taken in maximum light condition produces descent pics but struggles in low light condition. hdr mode is average. it can shoot videos in full hd resolution. electronic image stabilizer (eis) minimizes shakiness of video and camera autofocus feature also works fast. video quality is below average. front camera is of same resolution but do better job than rear camera. selfies taken in good light condition came impressive. you can easily post your selfies on social networking site. slefies does not contain detailing but they are looks good. selfies in low light condition are average. it can shoot video in 480p through front camera and quality is little bit better than rear camera. 5) battery life battery size is of 2450mah and its good for this price segment. it takes nearly 2 hours to fully charge it as it does not support fast charging feature. adapter is of 1a. battery easily last for full day on moderate usage. stand by mode is very impressive. battery percentage showing is not accurate. it seems times your ba